{
  "stem": "27509.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That had nothing to do-- as long as-- as life in terms of-- of the internal was going on, what was between man and man and between man and God were two separate things.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They are-- you know, the believing man has got-- does not exchange values.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are not-- they are not equating it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There are no exchanges.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There are no-- no quid pro quo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It changed firstly-- firstly changed when the Russians crossed the border in-- I called it the Agreement of-- the Molotov Agreement and started occupying their part of Poland which was allotted to them by that agreement.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have taken Bialystok.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They've taken it in a orderly, exemplary fashion.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been the 21st, the 22nd of-- of September.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Took three weeks--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--if not earlier.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The immediate results of that takeover is--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--of-- of-- of that occupation is extraordinarily worth recalling.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Within 24 hours of occupying Bialystok, the Chamber of Manufacturers, on instructions from the military-- the German military-- called all members of-- of the-- of the Chamber to a meeting.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a German officer addressed the meeting and said to the people, you are instructed-- you are ordered-- to open up your factories immediately.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You will continue with your production.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You will be provided with the raw material necessary for the type of goods that the German army requires.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The bank-- the national bank-- will be instrumental in ensuring that you have got the cash flow to pay the wages to the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And so it was.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was no question of if or what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The next day everything went back to-- to the status quo because it wasn't a question of selling the goods.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
